# LMHY Stack Health Loop

Recurring **outer loop** for integration wiring. Complements `lmhy-engagement-loop.mdc`.

> "I don't prompt Claude anymore. I write loops." — [Boris Cherny](https://x.com/bcherny/status/2038454341884154269)

## Stack endpoints

| Check | URL |
|-------|-----|
| Health + advisor | `GET /api/health/stack?advise=1` |
| Cron outer loop | `GET /api/cron/stack-loop` (Bearer `CRON_SECRET`) |
| Notion bootstrap | `GET /api/cron/bootstrap-notion` (Bearer `CRON_SECRET`) |
| SMS webhook | `POST /api/webhooks/sms` |
| Lead capture | `POST /api/leads/capture` |

## Boris Cherny-style `/loop` commands

```text
/loop 1d LMHY stack: GET https://www.letmehelpyourealtor.com/api/health/stack?advise=1; implement top advisor.actions[0] only; verify successCriteria.
```

```text
/loop 6h LMHY GSC: audit lib/gsc-index-pages.ts canonicals on www; fix one GSC error class per pass.
```

```text
/loop 1d LMHY engagement: homepage + /contact CTAs, LeadCaptureForm, AIChatWidget, MobileStickyCTA — one gap per pass.
```

## Each stack pass

1. **Discover** — health + advisor JSON
2. **One fix** — smallest effort that unblocks leads (Karpathy discipline)
3. **Checker** — re-run health; type-check if code changed
4. **State** — update `docs/LOOP-STATE.md` when priority shifts

## Priority order

1. FUB (`followUpBoss`)
2. Notion (`notionLeads` + valid `NOTION_TOKEN`)
3. Twilio signature when `smsAutoReply` is on
4. Turnstile
5. Engagement / GSC loops

